<h2><a name="CONF"></a>Student conferences and summer schools</h2>

<h3>International</h3>
<ul>
<li> <a 
href="http://www.associationforcomputationallinguistics.org/acl2005/index.php?studentws"><b>Student 
Research Workshop</b></a> at <a href="http://www.aclweb.org/acl2005/"><b>ACL-05</b></a>
<li> <a href="http://www.sissa.it/~gervain/StuS.html">Student Session</a> at <a 
href="http://www.macs.hw.ac.uk/esslli05/">ESSLLI 2005</a>
<li> <a href="http://www.linguistics.rub.de/FallSchool/">Computational Linguistics Fall School</a> 
at Ruhr-Universität Bochum
<li> <a href="http://lacl.labri.fr/student-session/">Student Session</a> at <a 
href="http://lacl.labri.fr/">LACL'2005</a> Logical Aspects of Computational Linguistics
<li> <a href="http://www.cs.ubbcluj.ro/eurolan2005">Eurolan 2005</a> Summerschool
</ul>

<h3>National</h3>
<ul>
<li>Germany: <ul>
<li><a href
="http://www.uni-koblenz.de/~koch/tacos.html"><b>TaCoS</b></a>, a conference for computational linguistics students
